Collector Service URLs:
- Production: https://volcano-audio-collector-production.up.railway.app
- Local: http://localhost:5005

Always use "collector" not "backend" in the production subdomain.

Available Endpoints (HTTP Method | Path | Description):
- GET /health - Health check (returns status, version, uptime)
- GET /status - Detailed collector status with metrics (optional ?timezone= param)
- GET /stations - List active stations from stations_config.json
- GET /trigger - Manually trigger collection cycle immediately
- GET /validate/24h - Validation endpoint
- POST /api/stream-audio - On-demand audio streaming (requires station/time params)
- GET /api/stations - List available stations (legacy, same as /stations)

Note: Use required_permissions: ['all'] when accessing these endpoints to avoid SSL certificate errors and ensure proper network access.